# Intuition

Count each row and col to see whether it is completely covered.

# Approach

Create a map from value to coordinate.
Iterate arr array, for each value, get its coord, then check that point is covered by either row or column.

If I use visited mat, it would get TLE.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(m*n)

- Space complexity:
O(m*n)

# Code
