Initially create a 2Darray that keeps record of row number and column number of a particular value that lies in the range 1 to m*n present in mat[][].
Create two arrays that will keep track of the number of elements colored in ith row and ith column.
if ith row or ith column becomes fully colored, we stop our traversal.

