# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Dijekstra algorithm: minimum distance between source and destination in weighted graph.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
create an adjecency list of all special roads. Other ordinary roads dist can calculated without maintaining it in adjecency.

in Dijekstra
after checking special roads
check dist from current node to every other node in special node+target node

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
worst case 200 special roads -> 400+2(source and dest) nodes to check, 

V: 402-->O(100) 
E:200+402*(402) --> O(100000) 

queue operations log(V) maximum V nodes in queue ie log(100)

complexity: O(E*log(V)) --> O(10^5)*log(100)
                          --> O(10^5)*6
                          --> O(10^5)


- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(V)+O(E)

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
   int minimumCost(vector<int>& start, vector<int>& target, vector<vector<int>>& specialRoads) {
        map<pair<int, int>, vector<pair<pair<int,int>, int>>> adj;
        multiset<pair<int,pair<int,int>>> q;
        set<pair<int,int>> nodes;
        nodes.insert({target[0], target[1]});

        for(int i=0; i<specialRoads.size(); i++){
            nodes.insert({specialRoads[i][0], specialRoads[i][1]});
            nodes.insert({specialRoads[i][2], specialRoads[i][3]});
            adj[{specialRoads[i][0], specialRoads[i][1]}].push_back({{specialRoads[i][2], specialRoads[i][3]}, specialRoads[i][4]});


        }

        q.insert({0,{start[0], start[1]}});
        map<pair<int,int>, int> dist;
        map <pair<int,int>, int> visited;
        dist[{start[0], start[1]}]=0;
        visited[{start[0], start[1]}]=1;


        while(!q.empty()){
            pair<int, pair<int,int>> temp = *q.begin();
            visited[temp.second]=1;    
            q.erase(q.begin());


            for(auto &i: adj[temp.second]){

                    if((dist.find(i.first)==dist.end() or ((dist.find(i.first)!=dist.end() and ((dist[temp.second]+i.second))<dist[i.first])))){
                        dist[i.first]=dist[temp.second]+i.second;
                        q.insert({dist[i.first], i.first});
                    }
            }

            for(auto &i: nodes){
                if((dist.find(i)==dist.end() or ((dist.find(i)!=dist.end() and ((dist[temp.second]+abs(temp.second.first-i.first)+abs(temp.second.second-i.second)))<dist[i])))){

                            dist[i]=dist[temp.second]+abs(temp.second.first-i.first)+abs(temp.second.second-i.second);
                            q.insert({dist[i], i});
                 }
            }            
        }


        return dist[{target[0], target[1]}];   
    }
};
